definition: end/conclusion/to come to an end/to terminate (sth)
(of a plant) to produce (fruit or seeds)/Taiwan pr. [jie2]
knot/sturdy/bond/to tie/to bind/to check out (of a hotel)

sentences.english: Destructors or finalizers cannot be explicitly overridden.
sentences.chinese: 無法顯式重寫析構函數或終結器。

sentences.english: Gray-matter maturity, however, does not signal the end of mental change.
sentences.chinese: 然而灰質的成熟並不標誌着智力變換的終結。

sentences.english: This constant choiceless awareness ends all illusions and all hypocrisy.
sentences.chinese: 這種不停的無選擇的覺察終結了所有幻覺和所有虛僞。

sentences.english: If, though, this trait is too annoying, end the friendship.
sentences.chinese: 可是如果這種性格太煩人，那就終結友誼。

sentences.english: The hard fut battle for recognition has been won, but it is by no means over.
sentences.chinese: 這場艱苦的女性能力認可戰雖已打贏，卻遠未終結。

sentences.english: Doyle insisted his finishing off Holmes was a "justifiable homicide".
sentences.chinese: 道爾堅持自己終結福爾摩斯的生命是有理有據的。

sentences.english: The unfinalizability of dialogue forces reader to find the truth of the Sutpen s tragedy.
sentences.chinese: 對話的未終結性迫使讀者參與到找出真相的活動中來。

sentences.english: But that was not the end of the affair.
sentences.chinese: 但是這並非是這個事情的終結。

sentences.english: He has put over good final balls since the start of the season.
sentences.chinese: 從這季初開始，他漂亮的終結傳球會不斷展現。

sentences.english: When you get to the end of your route, turn around and walk in the opposite direction until you get to the starting point.
sentences.chinese: 當你的行程終結，轉過身從反方向走回你的出發點。

sentences.english: First, trade petered out and then ceased altogether.
sentences.chinese: 首先，貿易逐漸減少，然後完全終結。

sentences.english: A second legitimate use of finalizers concerns objects with native peers.
sentences.chinese: 終結方法的第二個合法使用是關於對象的本地對等體。

sentences.english: Chapelle demands that Mason immediately end the situation at the facility.
sentences.chinese: 薛潘要求梅森立即終結拘留所的狀況。

sentences.english: Mediation usually breaks down when parents argue about the "he said - she said" issues between them.
sentences.chinese: 調節經常因爲“他說過，她說過”而終結下來。

sentences.english: But the alternative could be the end of the euro.
sentences.chinese: 但是另外的選擇可能就是歐元終結。
